4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that allows students to start a career as a data scientist and build their first ML models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes weekly and a maximum class size of 12 people. No previous experience is required, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and gain proficiency in industry-standard tools. The course covers topics such as supervised and unsupervised learning models, predictive modeling, and developing AI projects. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. To learn more, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop